    {
      "name": "Acid Spray",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon makes a ranged attack against a target within Short range,&nbsp;spraying the target with acid. If hit, the target takes a 4/W3 Wound and must make a TN 5 Prowess&nbsp;saving throw. If they fail, they are covered in the acid and will take a 4/W3 Wound at the beginning of&nbsp;each of their following turns until they can remove it with a Full action. The acid is corrosive to&nbsp;equipment. The acid will slowly eat through layers of clothing and any equipment they were holding&nbsp;when sprayed. Any gear covered in acid will become Damaged after 2 Rounds and be destroyed after&nbsp;6 Rounds.</p>",
